metadata.name: KILLER GF GENESIS x laur
metadata.description:
This is the first KILLER GF GENESIS 1/1 charity auction piece, made in collaboration with the Killer GF team and laur, co-founder of [uwucrew NFT](https://uwucrew.art/). laur's charity of choice is [Adopt-A-Classroom](https://adoptaclassroom.org/), a national, award-winning nonprofit that provides funding for K-12 teachers and schools.

The KILLER GF GENESIS collection is a series of 7 1/1 NFTs, featuring some of the leading NFT artists in the space. All funds received from the auction will be split 3 ways, with proceeds going evenly towards the Killer GF team, the artist, and a charity chosen by the artist!

All bidders will receive a bid stamp as a thank you from the Killer GF team and laur.
